## Minimum “syntax you must know” (cheat sheet)
- `flowchart TD` = top-down flowchart
- `A[Box]`, `B{Decision}`
- `A --> B`
- `A -->|label| B`
- `stateDiagram-v2`
- `sequenceDiagram`

That’s… honestly 95% of it.

